Package: ucLoader
Title: Load Files from Databricks Unity Catalog into R
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: 
    person("Mackenzie", "Ridout", , "Mackenzie.Ridout@defra.gov.uk", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Convenience helpers to download files from Databricks Unity Catalog
    via the REST API and load them into an R session (e.g. read CSVs or load
    .RData files). Designed for use on RStudio Server / Databricks where the
    Databricks host is provided via environment variables.
License: MIT + file LICENSE
Encoding: UTF-8
Roxygen: list(markdown = TRUE)
RoxygenNote: 7.3.1
Imports: 
    cli,
    curl,
    getPass
URL: https://github.com/ridout-m/ucLoader
BugReports: https://github.com/ridout-m/ucLoader/issues
